N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 128.1 - Jury districts

State Regulations

There may be no jury districts from which
prospective jurors may be drawn consisting of less than the whole of the
governmental subdivision wherein the court convenes. Notes
